{"questionId": "7fac16fb", "correctAnswer": "69", "section": "Math", "steps": [{"title": "Substitute the value x = 20", "content": "Replace $x$ with $20$ in $$f(x) = \\frac{7}{10}x + 55.$$ This gives $$f(20) = \\frac{7}{10}(20) + 55.$$"}, {"title": "Compute the result", "content": "Simplify: $$f(20) = 14 + 55 = 69.$$ The answer is <strong>69</strong>."}]}